&lt;a name="rest_code_bc0755f94acc4ed8a1da6c80c1daf12f-36"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;show&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;In both cases the result is the plot below.&lt;/p&gt;
